                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The test OverseerCollectionConfigSetProcessorTest has failed 4 out of the last 5 runs, and last stable build is almost 2 days ago.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://ci-builds.apache.org/job/Solr/job/Solr-Check-main/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://ci-builds.apache.org/job/Solr/job/Solr-Check-main/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
